visible_df <- df %>% 
  filter((wavelength >= 380) & (wavelength <= 750)) %>%
  mutate(rigel_norm = (rigel - min(rigel))/(max(rigel) - min(rigel))) %>%
  mutate(betelgeuse_norm = (betelgeuse - min(betelgeuse))/(max(betelgeuse) - min(betelgeuse)))
